name: Sledgren's 'DARKMATTER' DrumKit
description:
Specially formatted atmospheric sound & samples with heavy emphasis on analogue synthesis. Including synth sequences, ambient pads, specially processed 808 drums, snares, one-shots & fx. Also includes Sledgren's previously released "Everything is Taylor'd" Kit (free of charge) these sounds are fresh for all styles of compositions. DARKMATTER will change your music forever!
Will be emailed withing 24hrs upon purchase
